spec_data.Name: texlive-ecltree
spec_data.Description:
The package recursively draws trees: each subtree is defined in
a 'bundle' environment, with a set of leaves described by
\chunk macros. A chunk may have a bundle environment inside it.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:37:11 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Trees using epic and eepic macros
